RelatedSentence: After the 20 - year - old Grande debuted Problem at the Disney Music Awards on April 27 , the song rocketed to No. 3 on the Billboard Hot 100 , dated May 17 .
Azalea 's Fancy , featuring Charli XCX , currently stands at No. 3 on the Hot 100 .
With Problem at No. 4 , Azalea is the first female rapper ever to have two songs concurrently in the top five of the Hot 100 chart .
